    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You receive a cursed digital camera that captures ghosts from a strange website. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The website allows you to liberate your loved ones by uploading images of their spirits using the camera. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You go to the nearest park where your girl was last seen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No multiple endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Length: 60 to 90 minutes, depending on your play style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Supporter content can be turned on and off in the main menu.</i> <i>(It is on by default).</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use the special camera made by a medium and find the ghost of your daughter, but an unexpected visitor might show up.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/bc6e3e9eed0cedec0ba7b231af825d65.poster.avif?t=1736470827\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/bc6e3e9eed0cedec0ba7b231af825d65.webm?t=1736470827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/bc6e3e9eed0cedec0ba7b231af825d65.mp4?t=1736470827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hint system: Call the numbers left by your daughter. She will help you find her through hints.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/197e0024b3a7a62895641d0bc2de5e56.poster.avif?t=1736470827\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/197e0024b3a7a62895641d0bc2de5e56.webm?t=1736470827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/197e0024b3a7a62895641d0bc2de5e56.mp4?t=1736470827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Authentic Japanese park</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/728a6a7dd30e3a7616736938de5f45f3.poster.avif?t=1736470827\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/728a6a7dd30e3a7616736938de5f45f3.webm?t=1736470827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334550/extras/728a6a7dd30e3a7616736938de5f45f3.mp4?t=1736470827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you encounter any problems, please try the following:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Make sure your hardware supports DX12</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>-Update GPU driver</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>-Lower the Graphics settings/Screen resolution and use upscaling (TSR, DLSS, FSR, etc)</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>-Latest Windows update</i></strong></p>",
